name: Friends Forever Birthday and Address Book (Original Design)
description:
You will love this cute and handy book! The Birthday section features a monthly calendar with colorful themes! The Address Book has at least two pages for each letter to record your friends info such as address, phone and e-mail! It also has pages for zodiac signs, special occasions, website logins & passwords.  You can use it year-after-year, it’s the only address book you’ll need!

Paperback: 132 pages
Size: 6x9

name: Friends Forever Getting-To-Know-You Journal (Original Design)
description:
Get to know your friends and yourself too! This write-in journal features interesting sections about family, life, thoughts on love, friendship and secret wishes! You will also discover your friends favorite things – books, entertainment, music and more! Fill out the first set of questions, then invite 4 of your friends to fill out the rest! It will be a great read and a cherished book afterwards!  

Paperback: 54 pages
Size: 6x9

name: Happy Girl ABC Inspirational Journal
description:
You will love this ABC Inspirational Journal! It contains motivational quotes starting from A through Z which aim to uplift your spirit and motivate you to achieve your goals and dreams. It is a journal as well with interesting guide questions designed for reflection and self-discovery. This knowledge can help give you the self confidence needed to become your best!  You’ll also realize just how blessed you are! 

Have fun & be happy!

Paperback: 86 pages
Size: 6x9
